Source file size does not exceed 30 MB (before compression)

Size of the game project exported from the game engine

Game main package size

The main package size does not exceed 4 MB (before compression)

All files in the game project, except those under `subpackages/*`, will be counted within the size range of the main game package

Independent subpackage size

The main package size does not exceed 4 MB (before compression)

The size of the package body defined as `independent: true` in the game subpackages

